* Implement Conventions\nAcross Organization
** Document conventions
***_ Central accessible location
***_ Include examples (correct & incorrect)
** Control access via permissions
***_ Limit CREATE TABLE / CREATE SCHEMA
***_ Domain-based catalog permissions
** Validate in CI/CD pipelines
***_ Automated checks before deployment
***_ Reject non-compliant names early
** Review existing objects regularly
***_ Use information_schema to audit
***_ Plan remediation for legacy names
** Balance flexibility vs standardization
***_ Strict for regulated environments
***_ Flexible for experimentation phases
@endmindmap
